{"tid":911604,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個見過毒撚做既柒野","createTime":"2018-11-22T04:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T08:48:43.000Z","uid":68626,"like":4,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0c7db315ed005eba66c876d60311cd5e30d26400","tid":911604,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"係好多年前 MOVENPICK仲未上位<br />\n哈根大師仲係平民學生TOP TIER雪糕個陣<br />\n我地一行8個人去食放題(D人我都唔撚熟 係隔離間唔中答一兩句嗲)<br />\n之後食到最後一人送一小杯哈根大師雪糕啦<br />\n咁我地就食啦 個毒撚話佢飽唔食住<br />\n之後將個雪糕放左入自己個初音背包到<br />\n話帶番屋企食咁話喎<br />\n我地成班即刻忍唔住笑<br />\n同佢講呢D雪糕好快溶 番到屋企都溶撚晒<br />\n之後佢個樣咁尷尷尬尬咁即場開黎食<br />\n事隔數年 諗起當初佢比幾個同學質疑個陣個怯樣都忍唔住笑"},{"pid":"bbe8807c33be39a0971bcb1ca281ec2b375b1a63","tid":911604,"uid":123264,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"分段不明確 節奏慢 故事條理不清<br />\n題材普通 無亮點 未改名就開膠post<br />\n2.5/10分"},{"pid":"009174eb26666cd6cbe4a0331257c52e8ec14191","tid":911604,"uid":31254,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"有條毒撚 喺巴士入面大叫 星爆<br />\n跟著全車靜左"},{"pid":"155e0565e272339289242d4e04fbfea23518166a","tid":911604,"uid":93649,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"上堂送花<br />\n但條女唔受仲好驚"},{"pid":"a6e897949e06378d84cbce8e45d258c61af8d4e2","tid":911604,"uid":161821,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"毒撚做乜都柒㗎啦"},{"pid":"aa775b63cca189a84a94cef9449fb75621bc8060","tid":911604,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"155e0565e272339289242d4e04fbfea23518166a","tid":911604,"uid":93649,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"上堂送花<br />\n但條女唔受仲好驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300bcf10fea724559ab002f5cbd195bdfac20873","tid":911604,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"155e0565e